mail-spamassassin: Mail::SpamAssassin (spam filter)
mail-spamassassin:
mail-spamassassin: SpamAssassin is a mature, widely-deployed open source
mail-spamassassin: project that serves as a mail filter to identify
mail-spamassassin: spam, also known as unsolicited commercial email
mail-spamassassin: (UCE). SpamAssassin uses a variety of mechanisms
mail-spamassassin: including header and text analysis, Bayesian
mail-spamassassin: filtering, DNS blocklists, and collaborative filtering
mail-spamassassin: databases. SpamAssassin runs on a server, and filters
mail-spamassassin: spam before it reaches your mailbox.
